```plantuml
@startuml leekoko_Java-Web

actor User
participant "Frontend (HTML/JS)" as Frontend
participant "Servlet Controller" as Controller
participant "Service Layer" as Service
participant "DAO Layer" as DAO
participant "Database" as DB
participant "External API" as API

User -> Frontend: Submits request (e.g. form)
Frontend -> Controller: HTTP Request
Controller -> Service: Process request
alt Data needed
    Service -> DAO: Query data
    DAO -> DB: Execute query
    DB --> DAO: Return results
    DAO --> Service: Return data
else External service needed
    Service -> API: Call external service (e.g. Baidu Translate)
    API --> Service: Return response
end
Service --> Controller: Return processed data
Controller --> Frontend: Generate response
Frontend --> User: Display result

@enduml
```